Package: rho.http.httr2
Type: Package
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Title: Httr2 and Curl Worker Transport for Rho HTTP
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Rho HTTP client contract in mirai workers.
    Complete requests use httr2. Streaming requests use curl's multi event
    loop to capture a response head and relay body chunks over NNG without
    blocking the calling R event loop.
